aplo-r:temporalExtent.Learner%20Cameron.Knowledge%20Graph.Knowledge%20Engineering%20Workflow%20Planning.Knowledge%20Engineering%20Workflow%20Planning%20Application%20Snapshot.2026-03-04T13%3A42%3A00Z%20to%202026-03-04T14%3A07%3A00Z a aplo-ont:TemporalExtent ;
